ivardefs.name: category
ivardefs.desc: Category of supply, e.g.  central, non-stock, etc. This is used to support work flows associated with the supply process.

ivardefs.name: deliverFrom
ivardefs.desc: Where the supply is expected to come from.

ivardefs.name: deliverTo
ivardefs.desc: Where the supply is destined to go.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Business identifiers assigned to this SupplyRequest by the author and/or other systems. These identifiers remain constant as the resource is updated and propagates from server to server.

ivardefs.name: parameter_
ivardefs.desc: Specific parameters for the ordered item.  For example, the size of the indicated item.

ivardefs.name: priority
ivardefs.desc: Indicates how quickly this SupplyRequest should be addressed with respect to other requests.

ivardefs.name: quantity
ivardefs.desc: The amount that is being ordered of the indicated item.

ivardefs.name: reasonCode_
ivardefs.desc: The reason why the supply item was requested.

ivardefs.name: reasonReference_
ivardefs.desc: The reason why the supply item was requested.

ivardefs.name: requester
ivardefs.desc: The device, practitioner, etc. who initiated the request.

ivardefs.name: supplier_
ivardefs.desc: Who is intended to fulfill the request.

properties.desc: A record of a request for a medication, substance or device used in the healthcare setting.
